---
title: Italian Lamb Ragu & Gnocchi with Parmesan
description: Warm up with this pillowy soft pan-fried gnocchi, coated in a rich, meaty and veggie-loaded sauce. Finished with a sprinkling of freshly grated Parmesan cheese, Nonna won't be happy her best-kept secret is finally out!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oregano-lamb-ragu-gnocchi-a6e72f7e.jpg
